  "prompt": "Who is Shahrukh Khan?",
  "response": "Shahrukh Khan, often referred to as SRK, is a highly popular Indian actor, film producer, and television host. He is widely considered one of the most successful and influential actors in Bollywood cinema. Some key points about him include:\n\n1. Born on November 2, 1965, in New Delhi, India\n\n2. Nicknamed the \"King of Bollywood\" or \"King Khan\"\n\n3. Starred in numerous blockbuster films across multiple decades\n\n4. Known for romantic roles in movies like \"Dilwale Dulhania Le Jayenge\" and \"Kuch Kuch Hota Hai\"\n\n5. Won numerous awards, including 14 Filmfare Awards\n\n6. Also a successful film producer through his production company, Red Chillies Entertainment\n\n7. Has acted in over 80 Bollywood films\n\n8. Known for his charming personality and global popularity\n\n9. Considered one of the most prominent and influential personalities in Indian cinema\n\n10. Has also appeared in international productions and received global recognition\n\nShahrukh Khan is not just an actor but a cultural icon who has significantly influenced Indian cinema and popular culture.",
